narratives.question_text: How would you summarize ECON 111 01 for a fellow student? Would you recommend ECON 111 01 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: If you have any interest in music, take this class, especially if you have played but have no music background. If you are coming in without an music knowledge at all, it might be a little tough, but it's doable.
Highly recommend it for any person who wants to learn about music. Great course.
This is a great course to take as a 5th class. It's really fun and enjoyable, and you learn a lot about the basics of music! The workload is very light, but still enough that you learn.
